nsitionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a>&nbsp;的<code><strong>oncancel</strong></code>&nbsp;属性是一个<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code>，它是用来处理发送给<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dialog\"><code>&lt;dialog&gt;</code></a>元素的<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/cancel\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">cancel</a></code> 事件的。</p>\n\n<p>当用户需要离开一个&lt;dialog&gt;元素的时候就会触发&nbsp;<code>cancel</code>&nbsp;事件。这个事件处理器会防止事件向上传递，因此任何父处理器都不会接受到该事件。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>target</em>.oncancel = <em>functionRef</em>;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>functionRef</code> 是一个函数名 或者 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/function\">函数表达式</a>. 这个函数接收一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> 对象作为它唯一的参数。</p>\n\n<p>每次只有一个&nbsp;<code>oncancel</code> 处理器可以被赋值给一个对象。你可能更喜欢用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></a> 方法，因为它更灵活。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spectable standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">备注</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#handler-oncancel\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">oncancel</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.oncancel","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/oncancel/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另请参阅","title":"另请参阅","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/cancel\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">cancel</a></code>事件</li>\n <li>HTML <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dialog\"><code>&lt;dialog&gt;</code></a>元素</li>\n <li>相关的事件处理函数：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/close_event\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.onclose</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"另请参阅","id":"另请参阅"}],"summary":"GlobalEventHandlers 的oncancel 属性是一个event handler，它是用来处理发送给<dialog>元素的cancel 事件的。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.oncancel","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/globaleventhandlers/oncancel","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/globaleventhandlers/oncancel/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers","title":"GlobalEventHandlers"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/oncancel","title":"GlobalEventHandlers.oncancel"}],"pageTitle":"GlobalEventHandlers.oncancel - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}